'''Tarek Alaa Abdelghaffar Elgebaly''' ({{langx|ar|طارق علاء  عبد الغفار الجبالي}}; born 5 January 2002) is an Egyptian [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[right-back]] for [[Egyptian Premier League]] club [[ZED FC|ZED]], on loan from [[Pyramids FC|Pyramids]], and the [[Egypt national football team|Egypt national team]].<ref name="WF">{{WorldFootball.net}}</ref>

==Club career==
Alaa began his career with [[Smouha SC|Smouha]], and was promoted to the first team in the [[Egyptian Premier League]] during the 2022–23 season. In September 2024, Alaa joined fellow Premier League club [[Pyramids FC|Pyramids]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://koraplus.com/article/61678/%D8%A7%D9%86%D8%AA%D9%82%D8%A7%D9%84-%D8%B7%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%82-%D8%B9%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%A1-%D9%85%D9%86-%D8%B3%D9%85%D9%88%D8%AD%D8%A9-%D8%A5%D9%84%D9%89-%D8%A8%D9%8A%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%8A%D8%AF%D8%B2-%D9%85%D9%82%D8%A7%D8%A8%D9%84-18-%D9%85%D9%84%D9%8A%D9%88%D9%86 |title=انتقال طارق علاء من سموحة إلى بيراميدز مقابل 18 مليون جنيه |trans-title=Tarek Alaa Transfers from Smouha to Pyramids for 18 Million Pounds |work=Koraplus |date=1 September 2024 |access-date=30 May 2026 |language=ar}}</ref> In February 2026, Alaa was loaned to [[ZED FC|ZED]] for the remainder of the season.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.youm7.com/story/2026/2/8/زد-يعلن-التعاقد-مع-طارق-علاء-قادما-من-بيراميدز/7298414 |title=زد يعلن التعاقد مع طارق علاء قادما من بيراميدز |trans-title=ZED Announces Signing of Tarek Alaa from Pyramids FC |work=Youm7 |date=8 February 2026 |access-date=30 May 2026 |language=ar}}</ref>

==International career==
Alaa was called up to the [[Egypt national football team|Egypt national team]] for the first time in March 2026. He made his debut on 27 March in a [[Exhibition game#International football|friendly match]] against [[Saudi Arabia national football team|Saudi Arabia]], coming on as a substitute in the 76th minute of a 4–0 win.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://akhbarelyom.com/news/newdetails/4795517/1/%D8%B7%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%82-%D8%B9%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%A1-%D9%8A%D8%B4%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%83-%D9%84%D9%84%D9%85%D8%B1%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D9%88%D9%84%D9%8A-%D8%A8%D9%82%D9%85%D9%8A%D8%B5-%D9%85%D9%86%D8%AA%D8%AE%D8%A8 |title=طارق علاء يشارك للمرة الأولي بقميص منتخب مصر أمام السعودية |trans-title=Tarek Alaa makes his debut for the Egyptian national team against Saudi Arabia |work=[[Akhbar el-Yom]] |date=27 March 2026 |access-date=30 May 2026 |language=ar}}</ref> On 29 May, Alaa was included in Egypt's final squad for the [[2026 FIFA World Cup]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://sportstar.thehindu.com/football/final-egypt-squad-for-fifa-world-cup-2026-full-confirmed-list-of-players-mohamed-salah-marmoush-in/article71040529.ece |title= Final Egypt squad for FIFA World Cup 2026 — Full list of players; Salah, Marmoush included |work=[[Sportstar]] |date=30 May 2026 |access-date=30 May 2026}}</ref>

